prompts.frontCover: Ultra-minimalist anime rom-com scene, flat 2D illustration. The boy, with a comically shocked and flustered expression, is playfully trying to catch the girl's hand as she giggles and dashes away just out of reach. They are depicted as simple, charming cartoon figures with clean lines and solid colors. The girl is wearing a simple casual outfit with a knit beanie, and the boy is wearing a basic t-shirt. The background is a clean, solid cream color. A cascade of stylized, minimalist pale pink cherry blossom petals and bright anime-style sparkle effects float whimsically around them, emphasizing the playful, romantic chase. The composition is dynamic and lighthearted. In the center, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, the text reads: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao".
